    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170640/extras/33a0a8574decb1697b9202d1b93d6b3d.avif?t=1763665108\" width=1200 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the realm of the Child Eater. Escape a Cold War orphanage in this 1-6 player co-op survival horror. Solve shifting puzzles, evade cultists, and survive the Child Eater’s arrival. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170640/extras/82fe5de35719f7f4ec38b698d086932e.poster.avif?t=1763665108\" width=792 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170640/extras/82fe5de35719f7f4ec38b698d086932e.webm?t=1763665108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170640/extras/82fe5de35719f7f4ec38b698d086932e.mp4?t=1763665108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>Escape the orphanage</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>Hide. Loot. Solve puzzles. Work together.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170640/extras/9b7cece3bcbe555b54589ce1ad3f95be.poster.avif?t=1763665108\" width=800 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170640/extras/9b7cece3bcbe555b54589ce1ad3f95be.webm?t=1763665108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170640/extras/9b7cece3bcbe555b54589ce1ad3f95be.mp4?t=1763665108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170640/extras/67a79dfe9ddda4519f6d8e12b49cfea6.avif?t=1763665108\" width=1200 height=200 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer co-op survival horror for 1-6 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Communcation through proximity voicechat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic escape room mechanics where every session is different: puzzle-chain system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A hallucinatory horror engine that blurs reality and fear</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hostile enemies: priests, nuns, cult monsters, Child Eater</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlockable collectibles, titles, story pieces and achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 playable characters with their unique abilites and progression</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Authentic 1980s eastern bloc environment, featuring pop-cultural and Cold War references</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170640/extras/ab1cacefd906cf67a43fd7e69d529004.avif?t=1763665108\" width=1200 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is set in Eastern Europe in the early 1980s. The orphans (players) must figure out how to escape alive from an orphanage that harbors terrible, evil secrets. The caretakers, priests and nuns, are members of a satanic cult and the time has come for the final séance where all the orphans are to be sacrificed to unleash demonic forces on the world and bring demonic power to earth by the &quot;Child Eater&quot;. Secret story elements are revealed by playing through the game multiple times.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170640/extras/1ea404a059474ec2971eebca5661aca0.poster.avif?t=1763665108\" width=800 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170640/extras/1ea404a059474ec2971eebca5661aca0.webm?t=1763665108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170640/extras/1ea404a059474ec2971eebca5661aca0.mp4?t=1763665108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
